Changing the speed regime is provided by the decision of the Kyiv City Council dated 9.10.2018 №1739 / 5803.
A speed of 510 UAH is provided for speeding.
It should be reminded that on October 29, the Verkhovna Rada approved in the first reading and in general the law of Ukraine On Amendments to the Code of Administrative Offenses on Establishing Responsibility for Violations of the Rules of Carriage of Children.
